"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-how-to-watch-olympics-cycling-omnium-live-streams-at-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A guide to watching the multi-discipline event on August 8 and August 11  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  The Omnium, a multi-discipline event, is an all-round test of a track rider's credentials at theParis Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the men's event taking place on August 8 and the women's on August 11, here's how to watch an Olympics 2024 Omnium live stream.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the Heptathlon or Decathlon in Track & Field, the Omnium tests riders over the course of different races - four of them in this case - and crowns a winner based on their overall scores across the board.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Formerly a six-race, multi-day event, from the last Olympic cycle it has been revamped and simplified into a one-day, four-race format.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the only individual event for endurance track riders at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dates:Thursday, August 8 (men's); Sunday, August 11 (women's)  Free streams:CBC(Canada),BBC(UK),Channel 9(Australia)  USA:Peacock TV  Canada:CBC,TSN,Sportsnet  UK:BBC,Discovery+  Australia:Channel 9  Watch anywhere:TryNordVPN, 100% risk-free  First up is the scratch race, a first-across-the-line bunch race, then the tempo race, which adds points for positions on every lap.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 1.268471212275815e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.592397868130927e-16, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999967612894, \"rank\": 3.017291808068746e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9957349850777437, \"rank\": 0.004282414276116461, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999978999767, \"rank\": 1.9629419672583472e-09, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the elimination race, where the last rider across the line every other lap must withdraw until one is left, the riders conclude with the points race, a longer affair where intermediate sprints are dotted throughout and riders can look to gain more points by lapping the field.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Themen's Omniumtook place on Thursday August 8 and saw an open and entertaining contest, in which Benjamin Thomas (France) overcame a crash in the final race to delight the home crowd with France's first medal on the velodrome.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.7746466892492642, \"rank\": 0.23636363636346383, \"text\": \"Benjamin Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9983641694986167, \"rank\": 0.0016257262576800152, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9983641694986167, \"rank\": 0.0016257262576800152, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's Omnium takes place entirely on Sunday August 11 in a lunchtime and early-afternoon session.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The session kicks off with the first event in the women's Omnium, the scratch race, at 11:00 local time (CET), with the tempo race at 11:57, the elimination race at 12:53, and finally the points race at 13:56.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.148298396404932e-38, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}, {\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\", \"score\": 0.999848768129392, \"rank\": 0.00015125474523256763, \"text\": \"CET\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This guide explains how to watch Olympics Cycling Omnium 2024 wherever you are in the world, including details ofhow to use a VPNif you are away from home.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling\", \"score\": 0.8201587937157669, \"rank\": 0.19044675914922257, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.148298396404932e-38, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more from the track, find outhow to watch Track Cyclingat the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC holds the broadcasting rights for the Olympic Games in the USA.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2462, \"end\": 2465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9625717953238194, \"rank\": 0.03888354582466062, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2525, \"end\": 2528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.99996537125367, \"rank\": 3.46299456482717e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics will be shown across several of the the broadcaster's television channels, and also on the network's streaming service,Peacock.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999969035777858, \"rank\": 3.09642828723227e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's and women's Omnium events will be available on Peacock, which offers a seven-day free trial for those who want to try before they buy.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999969035777858, \"rank\": 3.09642828723227e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A full subscription to the service via Peacock Premium starts from $7.99 per month.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"score\": 0.9999999936162567, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peacock Premium\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ad-free Peacock Premium Plus costs $13.99 per month.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The final rounds for each event will also be shown live on television, with the men's final on USA Network on August 8 and the women's final on NBC on August 11.\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3158, \"end\": 3169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.999293587106385, \"rank\": 0.0007069122655288989, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}, {\"begin\": 3207, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9625717953238194, \"rank\": 0.03888354582466062, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These channels are available via cable plans, but there is no need to worry if you do not have cable.Slingis a smart TV service that allows people in the US to watch cable channels on their TV, laptop or tablet without actually having to subscribe to an annual cable TV package.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3380, \"end\": 3382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9996645162586869, \"rank\": 0.0003355963181636224, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC and USA Network are available on Sling with the Sling Blue package, which costs $40 per month ($20 for the first month).\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3505, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9625717953238194, \"rank\": 0.03888354582466062, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3513, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.999293587106385, \"rank\": 0.0007069122655288989, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you live in Canada, you can catch the Olympics across several broadcasters, including the free-to-air CBC, and subscription services TSN and Sportsnet.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 1.268471212275815e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 3767, \"end\": 3770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.592397868130927e-16, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not clear whetherCBCwill show the Omnium rounds as part of its daily television output but the action is set to be streamed online onCBC Gem.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.148298396404932e-38, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to the broadcaster's ad-free on-demand library costs $5.99 per month, though the ad-supported version is free of charge.\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TSN and Sportsnet do not have dedicated streams for each sport, so it's not certain whether the Omnium events will make the cut as part of their programming.\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4063, \"end\": 4066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.592397868130927e-16, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 4159, \"end\": 4165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.148298396404932e-38, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheTSNsubscription service will set you back $19.99 per month or $199.90 per year.\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, aSportsnet SN Nowsubscription costs $14.99 per month or $179.99 per year.\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4327, \"end\": 4329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.763340786154912e-22, \"text\": \"SN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the UK, cycling fans will be able to watch the Olympics on the BBC for free, via BBC One, BBC Two andBBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4398, \"end\": 4400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999967612894, \"rank\": 3.017291808068746e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 4457, \"end\": 4460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9957349850777437, \"rank\": 0.004282414276116461, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC only has rights to broadcast two streams at any one time, however, so while the track cycling will be heavily favoured by the national broadcaster, it's not guaranteed that every minute of the Omnium events will be shown.\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4513, \"end\": 4516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9957349850777437, \"rank\": 0.004282414276116461, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For that, you will have to watch onDiscovery+, home to the most comprehensive coverage in the UK - 3,800 hours of live action across 55 channels.\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4834, \"end\": 4836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999967612894, \"rank\": 3.017291808068746e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to aspecial Olympics dealyou can subscribe to the \\\"standard\\\" Discovery+ package for a cut-price \\u00a33.99 per month - sign up before August 11 and you can take advantage of the lower price until the end of the year.\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 5105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The package includes year-round cycling streams as well as other live sports, including snooker, tennis, motorsports, and more.\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Australia, cycling fans can watch the Olympics for free onChannel 9and its9Now streaming service- arguably the most comprehensive free Olympics coverage in the world.\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5238, \"end\": 5247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999978999767, \"rank\": 1.9629419672583472e-09, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As is the case in other territories, a good chunk of the action is expected to be included in live television broadcast, but for guaranteed coverage of all the Omnium racing, fans can head to 9Now on the smart device of their choosing.\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are traveling abroad and try to access your usual live streaming services to watch the action, you may find your access to be geo-restricted.\", \"from\": 5643, \"to\": 5791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, a VPN service will come in handy, allowing your computer to pretend it's home and let you log into your streaming accounts to catch all of the racing action.\", \"from\": 5793, \"to\": 5964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our colleagues atTechRadarthoroughly tested several VPNservices and NordVPN won the gold medal:  NordVPN - get the world's favorite VPNWe've put all the major VPNs through their paces and we rate NordVPN as the best for streaming Netflix as our top pick, thanks to its speed, ease of use and strong security features.\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 6283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6196, \"end\": 6203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5121538587966907e-34, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also compatible with just about any streaming device out there, including Amazon Fire TV Stick, Apple TV, Xbox and PlayStation, as well as Android and Apple mobiles.\", \"from\": 6284, \"to\": 6454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6363, \"end\": 6383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Fire_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazon Fire 